{
  "stem": "3771.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "All this-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it just unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember I went home after work, and I got so hysterically in home that my mother didn't think-- didn't know what to do, what happened.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She-- I couldn't tell her what I have seen it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a-- for a few days, I was in a trance.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I couldn't get my senses together what I have seen it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, I just have told you, I think it was three or four episodes what I said.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I could tell you many, many horrifying more.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I have to admit to you, my beautiful people, shall your mind say to yourself, that you say to me, this is impossible.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It can't be.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's a horrifying dream, I would suggest-- I would have to admit you're right.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You're 100% right.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "If I wouldn't be there, and it wouldn't get ingrained in my mind-- in my thinking-- what I have seen, and I would be on you side, listening, most probably I would have said it is the unbelievable thing.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It is the unbelievable which the human mind cannot absorb.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It's not able to tell, to relate somehow, somewhere.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I, myself, even now, after so many years, I have a fight in my mind.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "For one side, the horror part, which is ingrained in my mind.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I wish I could press a button [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] and to be able to erase-- to erase that terrible cha-- [CRYING] terrible, terrible chapter.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I feel like that I'm-- my mind is not equipped.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It's not created to be able to tell, and to be the spokesman for all those horrifying things what I have seen-- not only in personally myself, for all the six million which they're suffering.",
      "word_count": 35
    }
  ],
